        <h1>Cancellation, Return, and Refund Policy</h1>
        <p>In keeping with FullRevMoto's goal of ensuring User satisfaction, any return or cancellation of Products by
            the customer shall be governed by and subject to the terms and conditions set out under this Cancellation,
            Return, and Refund Policy. Customers are required to read and understand this policy before initiating a
            purchase.</p>

        <h2>Policy Acceptance</h2>
        <p>By proceeding with a purchase on our platform, you agree to the terms of this policy without modification. If
            you do not agree with these terms, you are advised not to continue with the purchase.</p>

        <h2>Extenuating Circumstances</h2>
        <p>For circumstances such as natural disasters or medical emergencies, cancellations will be assessed on a
            case-by-case basis to ensure fairness and customer satisfaction.</p>

        <h2>No Cancellation During Promotional Sales</h2>
        <p>Products purchased during a “promotional sale” cannot be cancelled.</p>

        <h2>1. Cancellation by FullRevMoto</h2>
        <p>FullRevMoto reserves the right to cancel any order for various reasons, including product unavailability,
            pricing errors, or issues identified by our team. In such cases, we will notify you, and any charged amount
            will be refunded to your account.</p>

        <h2>2. Cancellation by the User</h2>
        <p>If you wish to cancel an order, FullRevMoto will assess your request. Orders that have not been processed may
            be cancelled, and you will be refunded within a reasonable period. Orders that have been processed cannot be
            cancelled.</p>

        <h2>3. Bulk Order Cancellation</h2>
        <p>FullRevMoto reserves the right to cancel orders classified as 'Bulk Orders' based on criteria such as
            non-consumption use, multiple orders for the same product at the same address, and bulk quantities. Promo
            codes used for 'Bulk Orders' will not be refunded.</p>

        <h2>4. Terms of Cancellation</h2>
        <h3>A. Cancellation Procedure</h3>
        <p>You can fully or partially cancel an order before it is dispatched by contacting Customer Care via call or
            WhatsApp at 8589020202. Please provide your order details to facilitate a smooth cancellation process.
            Refunds, except those credited to FullRevMoto Wallet, will incur a 2.5% charge for payment processing fees.
            For orders made using EMI options, related third-party processing fees will also be deducted.</p>

        <h3>B. Cancellation After Dispatch</h3>
        <p>We do not accept cancellations once the order has been dispatched unless there are extenuating circumstances
            as stated above.</p>

        <h2>Returns</h2>
        <p>Orders received must be inspected immediately. Any issues must be reported within 24 hours and returned
            within 10 days as per our Return and Refund Policy. We recommend recording an unboxing video upon receiving
            your package to assist in case of issues.</p>
